==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hartebeest
<hw>Har"te*beest`</hw></mhw>
<pr>(-b⟦emac⟧st`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D. <ets>hertebeest</ets>.
See <er>Hart</er>, and <er>Beast</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A large South African antelope (<spn>Alcelaphus
caama</spn>), formerly much more abundant than it is now. The face and
legs are marked with black, the rump with white.</def> <altsp>[Written
also <asp>hartebeest</asp>, and <asp>hartebest</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any anteleope of the genus <gen>Alcelaphus</gen> and
certain species of <gen>Darnaliscus</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Harten</ent>⟦br⟧
